title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Maa Beti
subTitle: Under her brother's influence, Laxmi mistreats her stepchildren, causing them to run away from home. His intentions are revealed when he throws her and her husband out of the house, destitute.

title: Ram Rajya
subTitle: Lord Rama returns to Ayodhya with his wife Sita after defeating Ravana in an epic battle. However, he exiles his wife when people start doubting her purity.

title: Doosri Dulhan
subTitle: A couple, unable to have children after a miscarriage, decides to hire a prostitute as a surrogate mother. However, they begin to face challenges that come with surrogacy.

title: Waqt Ki Deewar
subTitle: Two brothers are separated after their mother's death. Later, one of them becomes a gangster, and the other becomes a police officer, as they find themselves at odds, unaware of their true relationship.

title: Insaf Ka Tarazu
subTitle: Ramesh, a businessman, is arrested for molesting Bharati, a beauty queen. Later, she is arrested and tried in court for murdering him.

title: Ek Hasina Do Diwane
subTitle: Best friends Amar and Prakash love Neetu, but she marries Amar against her father's wishes. Their different lifestyles create problems and Prakash makes things worse.

title: Phool Aur Angaar
subTitle: A young man rescues a woman from being molested but gets accused of the heinous crime instead. Trying to apprehend the miscreants, he gets caught in a web of deception and lies.

title: Kohram
subTitle: Colonel Balbir Singh Sodhi assumes a disguise to unveil the true colours of Veer Bhadra Singh, a corrupt minister. Soon, Major Ajit teams up with him to execute the mission.

title: Aapas Ki Baat
subTitle: Kajal and Anand's love story is cut short after Kajal's family disapproves of their relationship. Years later, fate brings them back into each other's lives, but all is not as it seems.
